Package SingleWheeledVehicle

Class Monowheel

java.lang.Object
Superclass.Vehicle
WheeledVehicle.WheeledTransportation
SingleWheeledVehicle.Monowheel
public class Monowheel
extends WheeledTransportation
The Monowheel class is designed to contain the most basic attributes/methods which any monowheel vehicle should possess.
Author:
Kevin Courey
